Package local.intranet.tombola.api.model.entity

Class LoggingEvent

java.lang.Object
local.intranet.tombola.api.model.entity.LoggingEvent
@Entity public class LoggingEvent extends Object
LoggingEvent is an @Immutable entity for JPA with LoggingEventRepository

The entity without setters is only used to read data written by logback-spring DbAppender

https://www.baeldung.com/hibernate-immutable
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/67679636/spring-data-jpa-immutable-entity
